\begin_layout Standard
But from a statistical perspective, this makes our two-way fixed effects
 regression not work any more.
 The problem can actually so bad that, in some rare cases, you can get a
 negative diff-in-diff estimate even inf the true effect is positive for
 everone in the sample.
